casebody.data:
Mrs. Freda BOVETAS, etc., Appellant, v. UNITED STATES of America, Appel-lee. No. 6844. Circuit Court of Appeals, Ninth Circuit. May 16, 1932.

Before WILBUR and SAWTELLE, Circuit Judges, and NETERER, District Judge.

PER CURIAM.

Ordered appeal dismissed, pursuant to motion of appellee, for failure of appellant to file record and docket eause; mandate forthwith.
